[0.000, "o", "\u001b[2mI think I need to create a simple greeting without using any tools. I want to keep it friendly and structured in markdown. It makes sense to ask what the user would like to investigate in the codebase. I should keep it neat and concise, focusing on how I can help them explore the information they need. Let's get that greeting crafted!\u001b[0m\u001b[2m\r\n\u001b[0m"]
